{
  "texts": [
    "Regardless of the ultimate approach, some tensions are inevitable when contemplating how to safeguard fundamental rights, such as tradeoffs between safety and freedom of expression or privacy.",
    "Good regulation will have to carefully consider how to balance conflicting rights.",
    "We hope this work will support global, cross-sectoral discussions, in industry, academia, government, civil society, and other sectors.",
    "Our new extended reality depends on it.",
    "We use \"IXR\" as a generic term throughout or when referring to concerns across IXR, and \"VR\" or \"AR\" when referring to aspects of those specific areas.1 3"
  ]
}